    "description": "<br>您可以创建阿姆斯特丹、巴塞罗那、布鲁塞尔、伊斯坦布尔、伦敦、纽约、巴黎、悉尼、东京、威尼斯等宏伟城市的公交线路。您可以在晚上更好地看到这些城市的独特美景。在晚上，您可以更轻松地使用照亮道路的灯光创建新线路。.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288280/extras/7bf9ac9845ddab5b493611a34fda526b.poster.avif?t=1725027343\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288280/extras/7bf9ac9845ddab5b493611a34fda526b.webm?t=1725027343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288280/extras/7bf9ac9845ddab5b493611a34fda526b.mp4?t=1725027343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>您可以使用随机路径和您自己的设计智能来建造不同风格的道路。这样，您可以花费更少的资源并获得更多的结果。你可以用随机路径建造路口、桥梁、捷径和环路。.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288280/extras/8d125d8e21728e0fb2c6f9696c05cf54.poster.avif?t=1725027343\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288280/extras/8d125d8e21728e0fb2c6f9696c05cf54.webm?t=1725027343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288280/extras/8d125d8e21728e0fb2c6f9696c05cf54.mp4?t=1725027343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你不应该让公交线路太长。您也可以为此创建新行。通过这种方式，您可以通过正确使用有限的资源将更多的乘客运送到所需的站点。.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288280/extras/313de0b7f5073bf0a1ecdae7ccf23f72.poster.avif?t=1725027343\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288280/extras/313de0b7f5073bf0a1ecdae7ccf23f72.webm?t=1725027343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288280/extras/313de0b7f5073bf0a1ecdae7ccf23f72.mp4?t=1725027343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>您可以通过以适当的方式放置随机道路来在站点之间创建公交线路。这个设计模拟游戏中最重要的一点是有效地使用随机传入路径。.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288280/extras/337c62837ada43102773d2564ed400ff.poster.avif?t=1725027343\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288280/extras/337c62837ada43102773d2564ed400ff.webm?t=1725027343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288280/extras/337c62837ada43102773d2564ed400ff.mp4?t=1725027343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288280/extras/869d3a919db9ce11e4eee8fffb231c37.poster.avif?t=1725027343\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288280/extras/869d3a919db9ce11e4eee8fffb231c37.webm?t=1725027343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
